00:44:11.880 --> 00:44:14.280
We don't get confused
and lose things.

00:44:14.280 --> 00:44:15.730
But the idea of replicating

00:44:15.730 --> 00:44:19.420
over multiple storage environments
is going to have to be part

00:44:19.420 --> 00:44:23.220
of this archival process as well.

00:44:23.220 --> 00:44:28.570 position:56%
Then, we have this problem of making
