Some of you will be
familiar with publish

00:45:10.350 --> 00:45:12.330
and subscribe protocol regimes.

00:45:12.330 --> 00:45:16.520
And this feels to me like
it might be a place where,

00:45:16.520 --> 00:45:20.320
that notion could be used as
part of the archiving process.

00:45:20.320 --> 00:45:23.500
You know I declare this
