Some of them may ingest
the pages, some may not.

00:45:31.880 --> 00:45:36.640
They may choose to ingest pages of
certain type or certain content.

00:45:36.640 --> 00:45:41.680
We want that to be flexible so
that we don't force every archive

00:45:41.680 --> 00:45:46.350
to archive everything, but
we want it to be rich enough

00:45:46.350 --> 00:45:50.780
that we can archive almost
everything over the sum of all

00:45:50.780 --> 00:45:53.060
of the archiving processes.

00:45:53.060 --> 00:45:56.190
Plainly, we need a lot of
metadata and so we'll have

00:45:56.190 --> 00:45:57.610
to have a way to express that.

