and back to the virtual
machine notion.

00:46:19.650 --> 00:46:22.560
And then there's this
permission to use question.

00:46:22.560 --> 00:46:23.860
How do we represent that?

00:46:23.860 --> 00:46:27.620
How do we validate parties
who are accessing the content?

