00:47:46.050 --> 00:47:48.360
But I'd really rather have a clue

00:47:48.360 --> 00:47:50.230
that something is worth
snapshotting,

00:47:50.230 --> 00:47:52.170
as opposed to simply
taking a million pictures

00:47:52.170 --> 00:47:55.370
and hoping some of
them are appropriate.

00:47:55.370 --> 00:47:56.670
So, what else?

00:47:56.670 --> 00:48:00.480
Well, properties that would be
attractive, automatic archiving

00:48:00.480 --> 00:48:03.160
when you declare that
you're publishing.

00:48:03.160 --> 00:48:06.810
Is it a service that
you sign up for?

00:48:06.810 --> 00:48:09.550
How is that funded?

00:48:09.550 --> 00:48:13.020
What about registering
the software that's needed

00:48:13.020 --> 00:48:18.910 position:56%
to interpret the webpages, and a
permission system that goes with it.

00:48:18.910 --> 00:48:23.660
And now what do we do about stuff
