So, this is very much like
the digital realm environment

00:50:44.500 --> 00:50:46.810
that I imagine.

00:50:46.810 --> 00:50:50.360
And so, it could be that we have
in our hands some technology

00:50:50.360 --> 00:50:55.980
that will help us do this automatic
archiving and rendering of the web

00:50:55.980 --> 00:50:58.480
over time because the
