many museums around the world.

00:51:47.850 --> 00:51:51.110
And then finally, there's the
digital object architecture

00:51:51.110 --> 00:51:52.690
that Bob Kahn's worked on.

00:51:52.690 --> 00:51:55.950
And with permission, I'd like
to give you a brief rendering

00:51:55.950 --> 00:52:02.540
of that process, because I believe
it can play a very important role

00:52:02.540 --> 00:52:06.050
in the implementation of
the self-archiving web.

00:52:06.050 --> 00:52:14.680
So, in order to do that, I need
to go pick up these slides.

00:52:15.720 --> 00:52:24.820
Now, I should warn you that this
