01:13:52.780 --> 01:13:57.410
GeoCities.com, founded
in 1994, deleted in 2009;

01:13:57.410 --> 01:14:01.690 position:56%
saved thanks to web archivists, was
the kind of place where you could go

01:14:01.690 --> 01:14:05.800
and create your own website about
anything that you so desire.

01:14:05.800 --> 01:14:09.360
You'd go to GeoCities.com,
type in your email address,

01:14:09.360 --> 01:14:11.640
get your free megabyte,
two megabytes,

01:14:11.640 --> 01:14:14.430 position:56%
eventually ten megabytes of content.

01:14:14.430 --> 01:14:16.380
Whippy. And it was a big deal.

01:14:16.380 --> 01:14:19.030
And you could create a site
about anything that you wanted.

01:14:19.030 --> 01:14:22.260
You could create your love site
to "Buffy the Vampire Slayer,"

01:14:22.260 --> 01:14:26.630
your lamentation about the Toronto
Maple Leaf, your family tree,

01:14:26.630 --> 01:14:30.020
your love of Winnie the Pooh
if you're a 12-year-old child.

01:14:30.020 --> 01:14:32.530
And people took that to an extreme.

01:14:32.530 --> 01:14:35.740
And people jumped on
board with such aplomb.

01:14:35.740 --> 01:14:37.220
