on the Worldwide Web.

01:14:44.220 --> 01:14:48.670
GeoCities.com had its first
10,000 users in October of 1995,

01:14:48.670 --> 01:14:51.780
100,000 in August of 1996.

01:14:51.780 --> 01:14:54.660
A million in October 1997.

01:14:54.660 --> 01:14:56.960
And by its deletion in 2009,

01:14:56.960 --> 01:15:02.070
some 7 million people had
created webpages on GeoCities.com.

01:15:02.070 --> 01:15:05.460
