of everyday people.

01:15:27.370 --> 01:15:29.740
The example I like to make
just to bug my colleagues

01:15:29.740 --> 01:15:33.170
who do British history mostly,
is to say let's take your golden,

01:15:33.170 --> 01:15:36.150
