01:15:36.150 --> 01:15:39.240
if you want to study the 19th
century or the 18th century

01:15:39.240 --> 01:15:42.710
and see what it was like to be
an everyday person say in London,

01:15:42.710 --> 01:15:45.160
you have almost no information.

01:15:45.160 --> 01:15:47.670
You only have information
when people come into contact

01:15:47.670 --> 01:15:50.520
with the state, or the church,
or if an accident happens

01:15:50.520 --> 01:15:52.670
and something is left behind.

01:15:52.670 --> 01:15:55.770
And so, for many historians, they
reconstruct that sort of life

01:15:55.770 --> 01:15:58.620
