something like GeoCities.

01:16:15.470 --> 01:16:18.880
In short, historians are
moving from scarcity,

01:16:18.880 --> 01:16:21.530
where we used to have no
information about the past,

01:16:21.530 --> 01:16:24.540 position:56%
to abundance where we have too much.

01:16:24.540 --> 01:16:28.080
